title: Match History not working. Blank Display
body:
Match History site is only displaying a blank rectangle. I've tried clearing my browser data on different browsers and none seem to show the Match History. It's as if it was disabled.

http://i820.photobucket.com/albums/zz127/darian612/Match%20History.png

Any heads up on this?

Regards

Fernando D. Mata

replies.body: Can you provide the URL for the exact page on match history you're trying to access?

> [{quoted}](name=Targons Blade,realm=NA,application-id=osqw6G4M,discussion-id=kVmHEWpt,comment-id=0000,timestamp=2016-10-05T18:02:57.476+0000)
>
> Can you provide the URL for the exact page on match history you're trying to access?

http://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/

I'm also logged in on my user name

Thanks for providing that link. This issue sometimes happens depending on the browser used, browser add-ons, and if there are issues in the browser cache. I recommend first trying an *incognito* or *private window* in your browser since these often disable all browser add-ons. If that doesn't work, try [clearing your browser cache](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies) or using another browser entirely to see if anything changes.

Let me know if any of those steps worked for you.

No it's broken. I sent my friend a link to one of my matches. It only displayed properly for me, while logged into my account. For him it was a gray screen. For me, while in an incognito window, it was also a gray screen. Something is fucked.

I don't know what happened but it's now working. I had cleaned the cache before so I'm assuming it must have been an extension/add-on I removed at some point. Thank you for time and patience!

Regards

Fernando Mata
